data.description: FINAL CLOSE OUT - Kingman's only true gated community, CastleRock Village!  This gorgeous home is the only corner property left on Katie Lane.  This is a Travisto Model with an extended patio for great outdoor space.  This home boasts modern finishes, custom tile shower in the master, granite countertops and so much more!  For a small monthly contribution, residents enjoy a clubhouse, pool with solar heating for extended swim seasons, spa, bar-b-que, gym, meeting room and more.  Come visit CastleRock Village and see yourself in your new dream home here! Similar homes shown in photos, this home is under construction.
